                <r3d:remarks>The PolMine Project is now a registered CLARIN centre, i.e. it is listed here: https://www.clarin.eu/content/overview-clarin-centres. As a category C CLARIN centre, we offer metadata for the data resulting from the PolMine project that can be harvested by a web service.
